{"about_the_game":"Originally released on Nintendo 64 in 1997, DOOM 64 is an action first-person shooter and a direct sequel to the events of DOOM II. In celebration of DOOM\u2019s 25th anniversary, an enhanced version of DOOM 64 was released on PC and consoles in 2020 and can now be played here.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story </h2><br>Years have passed since you stopped Hell\u2019s invasion of Earth. Quarantined for humanity\u2019s safety, the UAC research facilities on Mars were abandoned and forgotten...until now. A signal from a degraded satellite suggests a single entity remains, and it has the power to resurrect the demons. As the only surviving marine who fought Hell\u2019s forces, you are sent on a lone crusade to hunt down the Mother of Demons and stop a renewed demonic invasion.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features </h2><br>Released in 2020 to celebrate DOOM\u2019s 25th anniversary, this enhanced version makes it even easier for players to enjoy the original game on modern platforms. Features include: <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Upgraded visuals <br></li><li> Improved mouse and keyboard controls <br></li><li> Gamepad/controller support <br></li><li> Widescreen resolution support <br></li><li> Native 60 FPS support <br></li><li> More than 30 action-packed levels <br></li><li> Additional \u201cLost Levels\u201d continuing the story </li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mother May I?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1148590/d4ffe18c23bcf67254f38b972e04284bb0a1927a.jpg"},{"name":"Walk the Path","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1148590/48d6c6fe6f0994c745a8ab0b2f175ce132a2d236.jpg"},{"name":"Secret Sleuth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1148590/423bf6aabeebecc33aa5d21a60a811f0fb224fd7.jpg"},{"name":"My Cause is Just, My Will is Strong","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1148590/a689